---
title: Honey-Glazed Pork Tenderloin with Caramelized Sweet Potatoes and Green Beans
description: The sweet and savoury combination of honey, thyme, and chicken broth makes for a delectable glaze over juicy pork tenderloin. Roasted sweet potatoes and green beans complete this delicious plate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/571a30104dab710e028b4567.jpg
